<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 09:14:07 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>由于对中国关税反应的担忧，欧洲汽车股进一步下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/european-auto-stocks-fall-further-concerns-over-chinas-tariff-response-2024-06-13/</link><description>欧洲一些最大的汽车制造商周四进一步下跌，原因是担心中国将如何应对欧盟委员会对中国进口电动汽车征收的新关税，以打击他们所说的来自北京的过度补贴。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 09:03:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/european-auto-stocks-fall-further-concerns-over-chinas-tariff-response-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>微软总裁将就安全漏洞向众议院小组作证</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/microsoft-president-testify-before-house-panel-over-security-lapses-2024-06-13/</link><description>微软总裁布拉德·史密斯将于周四在众议院国土安全小组作证，回答有关该公司在过去一年中俄罗斯和中国黑客入侵其系统后的安全实践的问题。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 09:02:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/microsoft-president-testify-before-house-panel-over-security-lapses-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>BRC 首席执行官表示，Shein 在加入英国零售集团时致力于可持续发展和劳工问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shein-committed-engage-sustainability-labour-when-joined-uk-retail-group-brc-ceo-2024-06-13/</link><description>该行业机构负责人告诉路透社，快时尚集团 Shein 在被允许加入英国零售联盟 (BRC) 后，承诺参与可持续发展和道德劳工政策等问题。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 08:03:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shein-committed-engage-sustainability-labour-when-joined-uk-retail-group-brc-ceo-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯在战术核演习中练习电子导弹发射</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-practiced-electronic-missile-launches-during-tactical-nuclear-drills-2024-06-13/</link><description>俄罗斯国防部表示，作为第二阶段部署战术核武器演习的一部分，俄罗斯练习了电子发射导弹。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 06:03:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-practiced-electronic-missile-launches-during-tactical-nuclear-drills-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲乳制品和猪肉生产商对中国对电动汽车关税的报复保持警惕</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/european-dairy-pork-producers-wary-chinese-retaliation-ev-tariffs-2024-06-13/</link><description>在欧盟周三决定对中国制造的电动汽车征收反补贴税后，从乳制品生产商到猪肉出口商等全球食品公司都对中国可能征收的报复性关税保持高度警惕。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 04:24:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/european-dairy-pork-producers-wary-chinese-retaliation-ev-tariffs-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>从西北到华东，干旱烘烤地区面临干旱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/northwest-east-china-parched-baking-regions-face-drought-2024-06-13/</link><description>中国部分地区连续数周降雨稀少，加上酷热，给多个省份带来了干旱，促使当局发出警报并采取行动，尽量减少对农业、水和能源供应的影响。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 03:42:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/northwest-east-china-parched-baking-regions-face-drought-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>受美联储前景影响，亚洲股市上涨，债券收益率下跌；欧洲走低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-13/</link><description>亚洲股市周四上涨，而债券收益率下滑，原因是投资者权衡美国通胀降温和美联储采取更强硬立场，但欧洲股市预计将低开。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 03:10:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>军政府向缅甸叛乱分子学习，建立新的中国无人机舰队</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/learning-myanmars-rebels-junta-builds-new-chinese-drone-fleet-2024-06-13/</link><description>去年，缅甸抵抗战士依靠分散的无人机舰队与东南亚最令人畏惧的军队之一进行战斗，取得了决定性突破。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 02:10:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/learning-myanmars-rebels-junta-builds-new-chinese-drone-fleet-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>七国集团领导人寻求达成协议，将俄罗斯资产的权益用于乌克兰</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/troubled-g7-leaders-focus-ukraine-war-china-italian-summit-2024-06-13/</link><description>七国集团领导人周四将在意大利南部举行年度峰会，旨在增加对乌克兰与俄罗斯战争的资金支持，并在对抗中国的政治和经济野心方面团结一致。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 01:04:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/troubled-g7-leaders-focus-ukraine-war-china-italian-summit-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>美元在利率驱动下上涨；日元在日本央行之前脆弱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-slips-cooler-us-inflation-yen-fragile-ahead-boj-2024-06-13/</link><description>美元周四小幅上涨，收复了前一天的部分跌幅，此前美联储预测今年仅降息一次，不过低于预期的美国通胀抑制了部分涨幅。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 00:58:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-slips-cooler-us-inflation-yen-fragile-ahead-boj-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国敦促欧盟扭转电动汽车关税的“错误方向”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-hopes-eu-will-reconsider-ev-tariffs-state-media-reports-2024-06-13/</link><description>据官方通讯社新华社报道，北京希望欧盟重新考虑对中国电动汽车的关税，并停止在“错误的方向”上进一步发展，以保护其汽车行业免受竞争。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 00:15:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-hopes-eu-will-reconsider-ev-tariffs-state-media-reports-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>李总理访问期间中国和新西兰深化贸易关系并讨论人权问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-premier-li-lands-new-zealand-talks-with-prime-minister-2024-06-12/</link><description>周四，在李强总理访问新西兰期间，新西兰和中国签署了贸易和气候变化协议，人权问题也被列入议程，这是中国七年来对新西兰的最高级别访问。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 23:17:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-premier-li-lands-new-zealand-talks-with-prime-minister-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>美国立法者在科学协议谈判中寻求中国专利数据</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-lawmakers-seek-china-patent-data-amid-science-pact-talks-2024-06-12/</link><description>共和党议员周三询问美国商务部，美国政府是否资助了获得中国专利的研究，旨在强调他们认为续签双边科技协议的风险。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 22:06:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-lawmakers-seek-china-patent-data-amid-science-pact-talks-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>早盘买盘：美国通货紧缩利好，中国通货紧缩利空</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-12/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 21:48:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>美国祝愿印度在紧张的中美关系中解决“结构性问题”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-wishes-india-luck-with-structural-issues-strained-china-ties-2024-06-12/</link><description>这位美国第二号外交官周三表示，美国祝愿印度努力改善与中国的紧张关系，同时警告说，中国领导人习近平发现很难在领土问题上表现出任何灵活性。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 21:41:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-wishes-india-luck-with-structural-issues-strained-china-ties-2024-06-12/</guid></item></channel></rss>